*jddayofweek*

(PHP 4, PHP 5, PHP 7, PHP 8)

jddayofweek â€” Returns the day of the week

===============================================================================
[ Description ]

  jddayofweek(int $julian_day, int $mode = CAL_DOW_DAYNO): int|string~

Returns the day of the week. Can return a string or an integer depending on the
mode.

===============================================================================
[ Parameters ]

{julian_day}

  A julian day number as integer

{mode}

                              Calendar week modes
     Mode                                 Meaning
  0          Return the day number as an int (0=Sunday, 1=Monday, etc)
  (Default)
  1          Returns string containing the day of week (English-Gregorian)
  2          Return a string containing the abbreviated day of week
             (English-Gregorian)

===============================================================================
[ Return Values ]

The gregorian weekday as either an integer or string.


